#. (itstool) path: page/p
#: ../help/C/cropping.page:20
msgid "Once you have done a preview scan, you need to define the area for the final scan. You can inspect the preview image and decide which part of the image you want to keep. Press the <gui>Pan</gui> button located below the preview image and then pan the image by dragging it with the mouse. Zoom in or out using the <keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>Mouse Wheel</key></keyseq>."
msgstr ""

